arguments.name: fromId
arguments.description: The ID of the user that originally sent the message

arguments.name: fromName
arguments.description: The name of the user that originally sent the message

arguments.name: channelPost
arguments.description: ID of the channel message that was forwarded

arguments.name: postAuthor
arguments.description: For channels and if signatures are enabled, author of the channel message

arguments.name: savedFromPeer
arguments.description: Only for messages forwarded to the current user (inputPeerSelf), full info about the user/channel that originally sent the message

arguments.name: savedFromMsgId
arguments.description: Only for messages forwarded to the current user (inputPeerSelf), ID of the message that was forwarded from the original user/channel
